{"tid":1807493,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點樣防止警甴餓底混入人群引大家捉鬼？","createTime":"2020-01-02T00:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T13:50:18.000Z","uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"171a4259e44a46832c1f66a5168ac431c1594845","tid":1807493,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T00:27:27.000Z","msg":"捉人者要比人捉返？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府正用盡一切手段迫企業歸邊，為示威者樹敵，為求社會各界與抗爭人士割蓆<br />\n<br />\n警謊「自己人」裝修銀行為由，中斷民陣元旦百萬人遊行<br />\n<br />\n比你捉到便衣狗係為咗養成捉鬼文化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6wEt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6wEt9.jpg&h=75dfc14f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好唔記得831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f82ba50df7d1248339f66eab0302eb9bd6dd279d","tid":1807493,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T00:35:41.000Z","msg":"幫你養成捉鬼文化<br />\n最後就互相猜疑，分割<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左貼文宣，仲可以試下呢個 零成本方法<br />\n<br />\n👇👇👇<br />\n請幫推，連儂牆 外既新動員方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1806977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1806977</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4b10794c073624c66d2c5a5b3a9bd867a77486c3","tid":1807493,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T00:46:04.000Z","msg":"個個行過都掉舊垃圾入去裝修，個個都大叫自己人咪冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21038ecf4670274e68c882c3581101fea95bd106","tid":1807493,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"